{"tid":8944,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（又有人失業）渣打又炒人","createTime":"2016-11-28T13:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T09:54:38.000Z","uid":3467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2559e6cfa56438ee4a2d4373a9bd2d37ee5dac96","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"渣打（2888）裁員瘦身行動始於2014年下半年開始，當時宣布全球裁減2000職位，翌年1月更宣布結束投行業務，全球裁200人，當中渣打香港則炒百人。同年二月集團大地震，6名董事會成員要「執包袱」，包括行政總裁冼博德。而新CEO 溫拓思6月上場，陸續執行2017年要節省18億美元的計劃。同年9月，渣打全球裁減約250名中高層董事總經理，香港亦受影響。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，渣打股價自2010年11月高見229元後輾轉回落，2015年初股價失守100元關，及至今年2月下旬，更低見42.7元低位，五年間高位跌了超過八成。期後股價反彈，今日收報61.4元，較2月低位反彈約四成，全年計仍跌約6%跑輸大市，較六年前則回吐約73%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161128&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55978125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161128%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55978125&d=Hc1%2BdZ9%2BT6jd8PNkX1crpsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=a118c6ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161128%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55978125&h=08d7aa57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161128&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55978125</a><br />\n裁員不絕又大地震　渣打股價六年跌73%"},{"pid":"c5b7e03a364f016207f584aa3c4449d728ee5d41","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"慘啦慘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51756e6b33a5913f93a1690479769769eeed5dbc","tid":8944,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"又炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38449170c05e9e9394e87da30e0f5485e3a453d3","tid":8944,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔炒港豬唔通炒其他區咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68cd24215f727054969e941f8a88cc573dd085e","tid":8944,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"唔炒又點有錢用contract去請班新仔<br />\n又慳到錢又cut到人手"},{"pid":"b3eb1efab4227d694d7eceddbaea2b05cf9b0f69","tid":8944,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔炒又點有錢用contract去請班新仔<br />\n又慳到錢又cut到人手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打熟行情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8732a17ce14946637389d53709d4aa2961ec87","tid":8944,"uid":24527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"其實香港影不大，聽講過入面做既人跳到既早就跳哂，剩返既人唔多deal做，而且渣打而家都唔敢咁博搵deal做。<br />\n<br />\n所以對香港企銀失業影響唔係咁大，用黎托下肌口價且"},{"pid":"ab0da2ad4d5a28e7633f49706ff374ab0f1acf0e","tid":8944,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ffa6226ece9e15536ff8a1ebb6cf1ee682aedc","tid":8944,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6f2734ccee572d60d1aca54d8657deffa1ce61","tid":8944,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"間間銀行炒人香港一定係炒最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378286e78d301067ac0c1e5344800a00fb2aa6de","tid":8944,"uid":32391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"全球裁200人，當中渣打香港則炒百人。<br />\n<br />\n笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee3084a0d87cf710a32520a3ab7c2ef44f03997","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔炒你香港人炒邊個呀"},{"pid":"d710f865f84c3771fa7dc2c20781fa99a3702fbf","tid":8944,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd06be463ab58f0a2c9b949025bc3174c2cfa69","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"應該陸續有黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9b832b0e832c116dc3f6ef96d44588f6a2b44b","tid":8944,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"炒多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb95bdc1fef3ec387740a66d0556dbe2338e0be","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:09:31.000Z","msg":"期待其他銀行接棒一齊炒炒炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753d7e2530e31aec222754185787c467309373f4","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"【更新內容】財金界近日炒味甚濃，不過喺「炒魷」個炒。繼渣打擬裁減一成人手，今日又傳出星展在亞洲裁員，以及瑞信有意裁過百名員工。本報收到市場消息，傳瑞信昨日已靜雞雞喺香港炒咗約80人！除了香港之外，《彭博》引述知情人士透露，為降低成本，瑞信今個星期將在倫敦裁員大約175人。"},{"pid":"03f5dc9f527f3d4dde1c05a3a10555062f60026f","tid":8944,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f01cadd9b0013617b28a4ed07080e5073ee25bc1","tid":8944,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港冇工會集體談判權 梗係搵港豬開刀啦！</span>"},{"pid":"57e53dd9ab34b598c87ebf192060e54e6ffec22e","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"市況不景，年尾分花紅前夕，一星期內有4間投行炒人！繼本周渣打、星展唯高達、瑞信倫敦接連傳出裁員後，昨日市傳法巴、瑞信香港亦出手裁員，一星期起碼300名投行員工失業，業界相信裁員潮延續至明年。"},{"pid":"91430ed0cc3e0ddab8f3fa294b479a689c997f2d","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"另有現職中資基金的前投行人士表示，成交低落、經濟前景不穩，令投行經營環境受壓，除大規模裁員受公眾注目之外，「時不時都逐少炒人，獵頭公司個個禮拜都收到一堆（求職者）名，股票部係重災區」，被裁者多屬高薪一族，大市淡靜之下難以維繫，他認為「炒咗咁多高人工嘅賓架出嚟，對消費、樓價一定有影響。」至於明年環球經濟普遍疲弱，他認為裁員潮延續至明年早已「預咗」。"},{"pid":"7783ec8b245f08f0168fc412d85d27959e895a43","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161203&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55997726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161203%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55997726&d=Hc1%2BdZ9%2BT6jd8PNkX1crpsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=92e56df9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161203%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55997726&h=90c1c737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161203&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55997726</a><br />\n【B1頭條】四投行一周炒300人"},{"pid":"bc9fc9a695c2e1c6c4f6efc3a48e0f6cd9c7a39e","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0206d7dd7c615d57b380874ba15119a49bb1b2","tid":8944,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"大飛俠林燕玲冇過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce461944540302a9825a964b364e13915b05acdd","tid":8944,"uid":3467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大飛俠林燕玲冇過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵緊工掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}